From 23879e123cec2048f31512f78b8eb7a87f8142ba Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Anthony Lazara <me@a5y.rocks>
Date: Sun, 22 Mar 2026 04:55:45 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] about: remove donate row from about panel

removes the donation row from the `About` panel and related localization strings. 
No shade to the GNOME project, they're great and you should definitely support them,
but the panel felt a little intrusive here.
